This project incorporates code from the following third-party repository,
which is also distributed under the MIT License:

  conditional-flow-matching
  Copyright (c) 2023 Alexander Tong
  https://github.com/atong01/conditional-flow-matching

  Specifically, the following components are adapted from or directly based on
  that repository:
    - torchcfm/conditional_flow_matching.py   (CFM training objectives)
    - torchcfm/optimal_transport.py           (OT-plan sampler)
    - torchcfm/utils.py                       (utility functions)
    - torchcfm/models/models.py               (MLP baselines)
    - torchcfm/models/unet/unet.py            (base OpenAI UNet + wrapper)
    - torchcfm/models/unet/unet_residal.py    (lightweight UNet variant)
    - torchcfm/models/unet/nn.py              (conv helpers, normalization)
    - torchcfm/models/unet/fp16_util.py       (FP16 conversion utilities)

